#. <CLT 04>図書館に着いた。<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Here we are at the school store...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>大きな建物の中には見渡す限りの本棚。<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>そのすべてにびっしりと本が詰まっている。<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Look at all this stuff. It's hard to imagine what they\n"
"*don't* have in here.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺たちの他に人影はないみたいだけど…<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>さてどうしようか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid "I want this awesome armor!"
msgstr ""

#. 勉強でもするか？
msgctxt "0004"
msgid "You want something like...that?"
msgstr ""

#. あはは、日向クンは真面目だなぁ。
msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"Wh-What are you planning!? Are you preparing to battle\n"
"with someone!?"
msgstr ""

#. 南の島で修学旅行中だってのに、
#. わざわざ図書館に来て勉強したいだなんて…
msgctxt "0006"
msgid "Do they have any new anime DVDs here...?"
msgstr ""

#. ボクにはとても出来ない発想だよ！
msgctxt "0007"
msgid "I would never presume to judge someone's hobbies..."
msgstr ""

#. キミがそこまで本気なら、
#. 付き合うのは勿論、構わないけど…
msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"...but if you want my opinion, anime is a total waste\n"
"of time! Stop watching it!"
msgstr ""

#. …本当に本気なのかい？
msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>How is that not \"presuming to judge\"...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 静かだな
msgctxt "0010"
msgid "You think there's any uniforms here?"
msgstr ""

#. そうだね。
#. やっぱり図書館は静かで落ち着くな。
msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"It's a school store, of course there are! I intend on\n"
"buying *that* here, if nothing else."
msgstr ""

#. …なんて、キミとボクの二人しかいないんだから
#. 静かなのは当たり前だよね！
msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"I need to get into this school's uniform and dive into\n"
"my studies!"
msgstr ""

#. キミと二人で静かなところにいるなんて…
#. あれ、変だな…逆に落ち着かなくなってきたよ…
msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 眠くなってきた…
msgctxt "0014"
msgid "Let's dig for treasure!"
msgstr ""

#. その気持ちは分からなくはないけど…
msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Dig for treasure!?"
msgstr ""

#. そんなに眠いならしかたない。
#. それじゃあ、ここからは別行動にしようか。
msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"Makoto! School is where you come to devote yourself to\n"
"your studies!"
msgstr ""

#. ボクは何か面白い本でもないか
#. 適当に探してみるよ。
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "This is no time to get addicted to treasure hunting!"
msgstr ""

#. よく燃えそうだな
msgctxt "0018"
msgid "That's a pretty cute doll."
msgstr ""

#. うーん…その発想はなかったな。
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"I have no desire to play make-believe. If that's what\n"
"you want, go find some little girls to play with."
msgstr ""

#. でも紙がこれだけあれば、燃やす以外にも
#. 色々と使えるだろうね。
msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"Besides, we're high school students, for gosh sake!\n"
"It's time you put away your childish things!"
msgstr ""

#. まぁ、そこまで過酷なサバイバルに
#. なるとも思えないけど。
msgctxt "0021"
msgid "I remember those toy vending machines!"
msgstr ""

#. でも、資材はあるに越した事はないし、
#. 日向クンは目の付け所がいいね！
msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"Hmm. Indeed, they're a common part of most people's\n"
"childhood."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>そんなに手放しで褒められると<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>落ち着かないな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0023"
msgid "But I've never touched one even once in my life!"
msgstr ""

#. 暇つぶしによさそうだな
msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"Still, I have those same fond memories. I saw a\n"
"classmate use one once!"
msgstr ""

#. うん、図書館っていくらでもいられるよね。
msgctxt "0025"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. それに、大人しく座って読書をしてる間は、
#. 能力に左右される事もあまりないし。
msgctxt "0026"
msgid "That's a huge vase!"
msgstr ""

#. ボクにとっては一番穏やかな
#. 時間の過ごし方かもしれないな…
msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"It's very large, you're right. And it has an air of\n"
"history that you can practically touch."
msgstr ""

#. ここに誘ってくれた事、
#. 感謝するよ、日向クン。
msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"I have to wonder how something like this wound up\n"
"here..."
msgstr ""

#. 特にする事はないな…
msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"Maybe they intended to fill it with flowers and\n"
"beautify the school."
msgstr ""

#. そうか…キミにとってはそうかもしれないね…
msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Or maybe someone simply brought it here to try and\n"
"sell it.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. ボクはわりと図書館って好きなんだけど…
#. キミと分かりあえないのは残念だよ。
msgctxt "0031"
msgid "Let's organize things in here a little..."
msgstr ""

#. それじゃ、ボクはなにか面白い本でも探しに行くよ。
#. キミはキミで好きにすればいいんじゃないかな。
msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"Organize, eh? Hahaha! You have a truly diligent soul,\n"
"Makoto!"
msgstr ""

#. よし、かくれんぼだ
msgctxt "0033"
msgid "Okay, let's work together to finish the task!"
msgstr ""

#. 隠れんぼには…
#. ちょっと嫌な思い出があるんだよね…
msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"No time like the present, am I right? So let's get to\n"
"work right away!"
msgstr ""

#. 何故かいつでも最後まで
#. 見つけてもらえないんだよ。
msgctxt "0035"
msgid "There's all kinds of paintings here..."
msgstr ""

#. これって不運なのかな？
#. それとも幸運…？
msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"As they say, to appreciate art is to develop the\n"
"heart!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>確かに判断に迷うところだな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0037"
msgid ""
"I feel like this painting realizes and recognizes that\n"
"sort of belief."
msgstr ""

#. よし、宝探しだ
msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"But to find it here in the school store... Is someone\n"
"trying to sell *this*, too!?"
msgstr ""

#. へえ…ここに何かがあるのかい？
msgctxt "0039"
msgid ""
"This is certainly a surprise! The scale at which this\n"
"school operates is simply immeasurable!"
msgstr ""

#. ボクがついてる限りは、
#. きっと見つけ出せるとは思うけど…
msgctxt "0040"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
